{"tid":2448113,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警犬咬傷油麻地61歲婦 右腳受傷送院","createTime":"2021-03-15T16:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T05:48:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":113,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec2eb02f78f92dbd9c56935ff3135a045ef45f6","tid":2448113,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:14:07.000Z","msg":"周一（15日）上午11時許，一名61歲女子在油麻地覺士道及佐敦道交界被一頭警犬咬傷，該名女子右腳受傷，清醒被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n該頭警犬為一頭雄性的德國狼犬，現正被隔離接受觀察。警犬隊正跟進事件。<br />\n<br />\n德國狼犬即德國牧羊犬，警犬隊成立初期，一如外國的警犬隊是以德國牧羊犬為主。警隊網站稱，德國狼犬性格忠心、勇敢、兼外型威武，是警察在巡邏的最佳工作伙伴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210316/RZ3U76TTJNDQ5L6DWBSX7ZEWIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210316%2FRZ3U76TTJNDQ5L6DWBSX7ZEWIE%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=c944aaca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210316%2FRZ3U76TTJNDQ5L6DWBSX7ZEWIE%2F&h=1f633bc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210316/RZ3U76TTJNDQ5L6DWBSX7ZEWIE/</a>"},{"pid":"142c3fe066de7a81c562c694fc1579805fd17a63","tid":2448113,"uid":2054,"like":299,"dislike":1,"score":298,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"以為黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcd60d2bad626ebea3dafcbecc4a670bc52f1a9","tid":2448113,"uid":58841,"like":196,"dislike":0,"score":196,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:15:10.000Z","msg":"我以為係邊隻藍衫狗咁饑渴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb407c6bfa88a385f243830914e74d6982efae1e","tid":2448113,"uid":164752,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:15:21.000Z","msg":"會唔會同隻狗拍針<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd006f19c6c60f4d23c30820